    "verse": {
      "index": 2058,
      "local_index": 2,
      "narrator_chain": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "قال السيد الرضي: وهذا مثل قوله (عليه ‏السلام): هَلَكَ فِي"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:322:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/469/596",
      "text": [
        "َّ رَجُلَانِ مُحِبٌّ غَالٍ ومُبْغِضٌ قَالٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "as-Sayyid ar-Raḍī says: This is on the lines of Amīr al-mu’minin’s own saying which runs as: “Two categories of persons will be ruined over me: the one who loves exaggeratingly and the hater and malicebearer.” [1]"
        ]
      }
